---
// This is the Battle Calculator content component
---

<section class="mt-12">
  <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white tracking-wider text-center">Battle Calculator</h2>
  <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 text-gray-300 tracking-wide text-center">Declare War on Math!</h3>

  <!-- Project Description -->
  <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed text-center">
    Are you tired of mundane, everyday calculators that lack excitement and engagement? Enter Battle Calculator, the app that brings a thrilling gaming experience to the world of mathematics.
  </p>

  <!-- Key Features Section -->
  <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
    <!-- Feature 1: Immersive Sound Effects -->
    <div class="bg-[#1b1b33] p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
      <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Immersive Sound Effects</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Each button press comes to life with corresponding sound effects. Feel the adrenaline rush as numbers are accompanied by thrilling shots sounds, and the calculation buttons detonate with an explosion sound!
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 2: Explosive Visual Effects -->
    <div class="bg-[#1b1b33] p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
      <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Explosive Visual Effects</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Prepare to be blown away when you press the calculation buttons. Watch in awe as a stunning visual effect simulates an explosion, turning your math calculations into an action-packed adventure.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="my-12 border-gray-600" />

  <!-- Visual Experience Section with Video -->
  <section class="relative mt-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white text-center">Feel the Sound and Visual Effects</h2>
    <iframe width="100%" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/axHB2DFny8Y" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen class="mt-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg"></iframe>
  </section>

  <!-- Buttons Section -->
  <div class="mt-16 mb-36 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
    
    <!-- GitHub Button -->
    <a href="https://github.com/jurilorenz/BattleCalculator" class="bg-white text-[#090a1a] font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-200 transition-all">
      Check Project on GitHub
    </a>

    <!-- Back to Projects Button -->
    <a href="/projects" class="bg-[#1f1235] text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full border-2 border-[#6d87d1] shadow-lg hover:bg-[#6d87d1] transition-all">
      Go Back to Projects
    </a>
  </div>
</section>